com.wpruszak.blitzch.beans

Class FileBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wpruszak.blitzch.beans.FileBean

  • public class FileBean
extends Object
    Simple file describing bean(entity) class.

    It contains all the informations needed to localize the file back and keep the file content in one place.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    setzo
    See Also:
    FileLoader, FileSaver
